Rules
[[Image:Rules.gif|thumb|RULES]]
Rules are a [[imaginary|theoretical]] thing invented by [[The Man]] to keep people away from the [[lulz]] in life. Rules try to stop you from doing all the fun, amusing and dangerous things that make living worthwhile, because they are all made by [[in the ass|anal retentive]] [[asshole]]s who have no life, and suck balls.

