*The man who lies with his father's wife has uncovered his father's nakedness; both of them shall be put to death; their blood is upon them. 
*If a man lies with his daughter-in-law, both of them shall be put to death; they have committed perversion; their blood is upon them. 
*If a [[homosexual|man lies with a male as with a woman]], both of them have committed an [[Juliana Wetmore|abomination]]; they shall be put to death; their blood is upon them. 
*If a man takes a wife and her mother also, [[GG|it is depravity]]; they shall be burned to death, both he and they, that there may be no depravity among you. 
